title: Offline_Explorer_Portable_6.7.4038_Multilingual.exe
description:
Extract and run OfflineExplorerPortable.
Language set by launcher according UserDefaultLang (if you don't want: write UserDefaultLang=false in OfflineExplorerPortable.ini): ar, cz, da, de, du, en, fr, hr, hu, id, it, pl, pt, ptbr, ro, ru, sk, sp, srb, src, tr, ua, zhcn, zhtc.
Settings of installed OfflineExplorer should be preserved.
